.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  以前唔知停完銅鑼灣村定美林村之後, 有路上到馬騮山, 但條路起尖山隧道果陣拆左"},{"pid":"6300e7584f462e9c37bb18df203cea66f27c2b34","tid":492171,"uid":41308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T15:12:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/n5d3hl9u\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fn5d3hl9u&h=45ec3578&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九巴81號往九龍方向<br />\n<br />\n美林邨同埋美桃樓只係對面<br />\n<br />\n想有位坐就美林邨，想快就美桃樓</blockquote><br />\n又係同一個方向行唒兩邊馬路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n路線歷史兼道路設計問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  以前唔知停完銅鑼灣村定美林村之後, 有路上到馬騮山, 但條路起尖山隧道果陣拆左</blockquote><br />\n係過左美林之後 有路上馬騮山"},{"pid":"ceb929b7b86296c298f34b0dde80bcc2b05dbe12","tid":492171,"uid":155246,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T16:38:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/n5d3hl9u\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fn5d3hl9u&h=45ec3578&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九巴81號往九龍方向<br />\n<br />\n美林邨同埋美桃樓只係對面<br />\n<br />\n想有位坐就美林邨，想快就美桃樓</blockquote><br />\n又係同一個方向行唒兩邊馬路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n路線歷史兼道路設計問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  以前唔知停完銅鑼灣村定美林村之後, 有路上到馬騮山, 但條路起尖山隧道果陣拆左</blockquote><br />\n係過左美林之後 有路上馬騮山</blockquote><br />\n以前嘅大埔公路大圍段，而家遺址就係落美林個彎位個山坡；以前大埔公路一路瀡到落去美桃樓，而家變咗駁青沙去市中心。<br />\n以前啲巴士喺再前一個路口先右轉去大埔公路去市中心，起咗青沙先改曬行橋底大圍道。"},{"pid":"6d1e35ab80f46d4d768a4c173111e51e60ce310f","tid":492171,"uid":41308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T23:23:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/n5d3hl9u\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fn5d3hl9u&h=45ec3578&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九巴81號往九龍方向<br />\n<br />\n美林邨同埋美桃樓只係對面<br />\n<br />\n想有位坐就美林邨，想快就美桃樓</blockquote><br />\n又係同一個方向行唒兩邊馬路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n路線歷史兼道路設計問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  以前唔知停完銅鑼灣村定美林村之後, 有路上到馬騮山, 但條路起尖山隧道果陣拆左</blockquote><br />\n係過左美林之後 有路上馬騮山</blockquote><br />\n以前嘅大埔公路大圍段，而家遺址就係落美林個彎位個山坡；以前大埔公路一路瀡到落去美桃樓，而家變咗駁青沙去市中心。<br />\n以前啲巴士喺再前一個路口先右轉去大埔公路去市中心，起咗青沙先改曬行橋底大圍道。</blockquote><br />\n最抵死既野係美田路專登整個位俾81號巴士掉頭。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60556469192bc3aa9535acc0e4194ee63f528a93","tid":492171,"uid":32175,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T03:53:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/13/115117_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F13%2F115117_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=06bd0d57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n摩士公園泳池，永光書院，天馬苑<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/13/115309_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F13%2F115309_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=19399146&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n反方向既有 龍翔官立中學， 黃大仙鐵路站"},{"pid":"01092357ca0df0df05c4882409a49f51c1317ee3","tid":492171,"uid":26361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T04:03:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>豐景園 翠